# Fake Images Folder

Place deepfake/AI-generated face images in this folder.

## Labeling

All images in this folder will automatically be labeled as:
- **Class: Fake**
- **Label: 1**

## Tips

- Include various deepfake generation methods (face swap, face reenactment, etc.)
- Various quality levels help model robustness
- Include both obvious and subtle manipulations
- Match the diversity of your real images dataset
